<div  about="/field-collection/field-mult-content/34" typeof="" class="ds-2col row entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-mult-content view-mode-full clearfix">

  <div class="col-sm-4 ">
    <h2 >Payment Obligation</h2>  </div>
  
  <div class="col-sm-8 ">
	  <div class="content field field-name-field-section-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><p>Registration via the UIC portal or any other recognized method of enrollment obligates a student to pay all applicable tuition and fees for the term. By registering for classes, you assume academic and financial responsibility for confirmed courses resulting from your registration and responsibility for any additional costs that may result from the University's efforts to obtain payment.</p>
<p>Your obligation remains unless you officially cancel your enrollment by the deadlines.</p>
<p>Note: Tuition and fees are subject to change without notice any time prior to the first day of instruction.</p>
</div>  </div>

</div>

